data.description: Welcome to your dream home in sunny Tampa, Florida! This spectacular 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem on a quarter-acre lot is the epitome of Florida living; with a canal at the rear, this property offers a lifestyle of comfort, luxury, and endless possibilities!  Step into your brand new kitchen, equipped with state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances like a new oven with a built-in air fryer, making cooking a breeze. The kitchen sink has a touchless faucet, adding a touch of modern convenience. The home has brand-new vinyl flooring with a lifetime warranty, fresh interior paint, and a 2016 split Rheem AC system. Plus, the bedrooms feature newer carpeting, and the washer and dryer do convey with the home.    But that's not all. This property boasts a pristine 6ft and 8ft vinyl fence for privacy and charm, and who could forget the banana trees? Adding a tropical touch to your backyard oasis. As if that wasn't enough, there's a canal in the back of the home with an old dock that can be restored to its former glory. Imagine the possibilities - fishing, kayaking, or just enjoying the serene water views right from your own backyard. And speaking of possibilities, there's plenty of room to bring your toys, and build the pool you've always wanted, this property has the space and potential to make that a reality.     Less than 10 miles from Tampa International airport, this home is conveniently located near Citrus Park Mall and Westchase area, known for its beautiful trails, parks, entertainment, shopping, hospitals, and so much more. You'll have everything you need right at your fingertips! No HOAs & CDDs. Don't miss this opportunity to live in a property with unlimited potential and an ideal location.     Buyer/agent to verify all information.
